<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ちくわ公式ポータルサイト</title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=M+PLUS+Rounded+1c:wght@700;900&family=Zen+Kaku+Gothic+New:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #fff9f0; /* ちくわの白身のようなクリーム色 */
            line-height: 1.8;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ちくわの「焼き色」をイメージした躍動感あるヘッダー */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a44 0%, #fc6076 100%);
            color: white;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 2rem;
            clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 0 100%);
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 200%; height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 10%, transparent 20%);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            animation: movePattern 20s linear infinite;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        @keyframes movePattern {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: translate(-50px, -50px) rotate(5deg); }
        }

        .hero-content { z-index: 1; }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'M PLUS Rounded 1c', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #c0392b, 6px 6px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            transform: skewX(-5deg);
        }

        .catchphrase {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            background: #fff;
            color: #d35400;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transform: skewX(-5deg);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'M PLUS Rounded 1c', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #d35400;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #d35400;
            margin: 0.5rem auto 0;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        /* ちくわとは？ セクション */
        .about-box {
            background: white;
            border: 4px solid #f39c12;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 5rem;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* キャラ紹介ギャラリー（仮） */
        .character-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .char-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #ffeaa7;
        }

        .char-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(211, 84, 0, 0.2);
            border-color: #f39c12;
        }

        .char-img-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background: #eee;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #999;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .char-info {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .char-name {
            font-family: 'M PLUS Rounded 1c', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #d35400;
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .catchphrase { font-size: 1.2rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>ちくわ公式<br>ポータルサイト</h1>
            <div class="catchphrase">ちくわはこの世で最も美味しい</div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">ちくわとは？</h2>
            <div class="about-box">
                <p>一見すると普通のちくわ。<br>しかし、変幻自在で相手に応じて<br><span class="highlight">21種類もある形態</span>に変化することが可能！</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">形態ファイル (全21種)</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">
                ※極秘データ受信中...（ここに画像が並びます）
            </p>
            
            <div class="character-grid">
                <div class="char-card">
                    <div class="char-img-placeholder">NO.01 画像準備中</div>
                    <div class="char-info">
                        <h3 class="char-name">形態 01</h3>
                        <p>詳細データ待機中...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="char-card">
                    <div class="char-img-placeholder">NO.02 画像準備中</div>
                    <div class="char-info">
                        <h3 class="char-name">形態 02</h3>
                        <p>詳細データ待機中...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="char-card">
                    <div class="char-img-placeholder">NO.03 画像準備中</div>
                    <div class="char-info">
                        <h3 class="char-name">形態 03</h3>
                        <p>詳細データ待機中...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div>
        </section>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
